    "Indeed, history has shown that e-commerce giants are sometimes caught violating privacy of their clients [37,44,90,102].",
    "This underscores the need for a deterrent and an accountability mechanism available to citizens.Privadome's threat model excludes drones that are not registered with the regulatory authority and other rogue drones that deliberately try to hide their current location.",
    "We also exclude from our threat model drones that use attached cameras that are outside of the purview of the drone's attested software stack.",
    "For example, a rogue drone operator can attempt to bypass Privadome by physically attaching a Go-Pro camera to the drone.",
    "Neither the trusted hardware on the drone nor the ROS2 software stack will have any control over such an attached camera."
